          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The photofission  cross  sections of U-233 and Pu-239",
                " have been studied by using monocromatic and discrete",
                " photons,  in  the  energy interval from 5.43 to 9.72",
                " MeV, produced by thermal neutron capture."
              ]
            }
